summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 4406 for the improvement of Woodland Park Avenue, from West Green Lake Way to North 85th Street; by the installation of a street lighting system; under Ordinance No. 52090, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
